    *    Schema for: Data Item CCR003 Consumer Credit data: Lenders
    *
    *    Version:    2
    *    Date:       01 June 2016 
    *
    *    History:    Version  2 follows publication of CP16/8 
                     Version  1 follows publication of CP13/10
    *                
